(This assignment explores embedding logic in a microcontroller to interact with hardware. Using an Arduino) Tj
T* (Uno wired to an LED and a push button in TinkerCAD, we implement a system that blinks an LED) Tj
T* (continuously while the button is pressed, and turns it off when the button is released.) Tj
ET
